folder: Tilden Street & Barnes Avenue, Bronx, NY
text:
Tilden Street (6-story building thereon), between Barnes Ave. and East Gunhill Road. The 6-story house is on the north side of the street and is called the Tilden Apartments. The view is northeastward from East Gunhill Road.

June 1, 1928.

P. L. Sperr.
